ro_Powered-by-the-All-New-Snapdragon-8-Gen-1-800x469.jpg 800w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/HONOR-Magic4-Pro_Powered-by-the-All-New-Snapdragon-8-Gen-1-768x450.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/HONOR-Magic4-Pro_Powered-by-the-All-New-Snapdragon-8-Gen-1-1536x900.jpg 1536w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/HONOR-Magic4-Pro_Powered-by-the-All-New-Snapdragon-8-Gen-1-1200x703.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> With the new HONOR Magic4 Pro, HONOR delivers best-in-class innovative technology while ensuring maximum privacy. Offering a groundbreaking new solution to sound-leaking, a common smartphone frustration for many, the HONOR Magic4 Pro debuts an all-new Privacy Calling feature supported by AI and powered by Directional Sound Technology, preventing sound leakage for more private phone calls. The flagship smartphone also comes equipped with an independent security chip, which provides maximum security for passwords and biometrics like face IDs and offers the world’s highest performing, thinnest and most reliable fingerprint security solution. The impressive design of the camera applauds the beauty of symmetry, which is an HONOR’s iconic design, also known as ‘The Eye of Muse’ – a 6.81-inch Quad-Curved display and ultra-thin bezels on both sides with an incredibly comfortable grip. The HONOR Magic4 Pro delivers a truly immersive viewing experience for all types of content including high-definition videos, high-tech graphics, movies, games and more. Perfect for those who spend long hours in front of the screen, the HONOR Magic4 Pro screen minimizes eye strain, even in low light environments. The HONOR Magic4 Pro offers effective protection against dust, rain and water, and is capable of being submerged in depths of water up to 1.5m deep for 30 minutes. As the latest iteration of HONOR’s flagship smartphone line-up, the HONOR Magic4 series benefits from the brand’s strong capabilities in R&D and not only signifies the team’s growth in product development but also demonstrates HONOR’s commitment to strive for excellence. With a wide range of compelling new features and functionalities including an industry-first powerful triple camera combination, 100W Wired and Wireless HONOR SuperCharge, latest HONOR Magic UI 6.0 based on Android 12, superior performance and comprehensive privacy features, iconic symmetrical design, visual experience enhanced display the HONOR Magic4 Pro guarantees an unforgettable smartphone experience for users. The phone will be available for consumers in Middle East in June 2022. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-435670" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Mr.-George-Zhao-CEO-of-HONOR-Device-Co-Ltd-at-the-event_HONOR-Magic4-Pro.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="424" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Mr.-George-Zhao-CEO-of-HONOR-Device-Co-Ltd-at-the-event_HONOR-Magic4-Pro.jpg 1769w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Mr.-George-Zhao-CEO-of-HONOR-Device-Co-Ltd-at-the-event_HONOR-Magic4-Pro-600x398.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Mr.-George-Zhao-CEO-of-HONOR-Device-Co-Ltd-at-the-event_HONOR-Magic4-Pro-800x530.jpg 800w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Mr.-George-Zhao-CEO-of-HONOR-Device-Co-Ltd-at-the-event_HONOR-Magic4-Pro-768x509.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Mr.-George-Zhao-CEO-of-HONOR-Device-Co-Ltd-at-the-event_HONOR-Magic4-Pro-1536x1018.jpg 1536w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Mr.-George-Zhao-CEO-of-HONOR-Device-Co-Ltd-at-the-event_HONOR-Magic4-Pro-1200x795.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" />